name: Travelection
tag_list: travel, travel-agent, travel-leads, travelers, tourism-marketing, tours
overview:
Travelection matches high quality travel agents with highly qualified travel leads.

Travelers submit a trip request, travel agents compete to offer the best trip for the traveler, then the traveler selects a winning travel agent. It is free for travelers to use and there is no obligation to buy.

Travel agents get free travel leads and only pay a small fee after they book a traveler. There is also a feature to add deals for travelers to view.

milestones.description: Launched a new feature to help travel agents do more with their travel agent marketing. They can post deals now.
